{"tid":1616550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因一次被習近平拒絕握手，梁振英處心積慮報復習，要習在世界面前難堪","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:30:59.000Z","uid":230104,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd287a90a06358aef8b0d00474c9b90d5a4da02b","tid":1616550,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/85KsHshWfnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F85KsHshWfnc&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=160aefd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/85KsHshWfnc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證據一<br />\n<br />\n退位者不甘被退位，對本朝特首既部下教育局長楊潤雄指手畫腳，甚至直接落命令左右佢地既政策<br />\n<br />\n犯左中國政治生態大忌，如果咁都可以，江澤民係咪可以對習近平既部下指指點點？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證據二<br />\n<br />\n當林鄭諗盡辦法為香港嚴重撕裂降溫既時候，梁振英卻挑起矛盾，最少七度發文指手劃腳，其目的顯然就係報復習近平：「你當年要我被退休，欽點一個廢女人執政，而家香港搞成咁，證明你選錯人，大錯特錯，只有我才有本事對付暴徒」"},{"pid":"c35319a714caec346b3aa37aee93d967d696aa18","tid":1616550,"uid":68009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"佢個樣唔似咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d94942563caee23c01b7d428fd6d2c67c9eb6","tid":1616550,"uid":65354,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/P1b356w.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/CXGzv2B.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"abf50ae968d987b0988da8fce0281cdea924bc3f","tid":1616550,"uid":274003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c35319a714caec346b3aa37aee93d967d696aa18","tid":1616550,"uid":68009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"佢個樣唔似咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"但係佢份人極度小氣又記仇，睇煲呔下場就知啦！"},{"pid":"a6297b1691d5c6aed3d35d0b7e8701beda3fed23","tid":1616550,"uid":230104,"lik